    <item>
      <title>Erja, 38 &amp; Lennart, 2 “I’m wearing an old Fredriksson cap, a Beastie Boys tour t...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWFj2IXAYGX/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/654197252_18578999941036149_6573984764963554428_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjY0NjMwNzM2ODIzOTUxMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxOC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=TCVxlbFH4mEQ7kNvwFwnQ8N&amp;_nc_oc=AdoNvweVEIRG3WS8jVMcwYS1DUu869_yLJCwfeMFNvOtApfaypfw_DJMkaWR3k1S49o&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=sd2RvPcYtCfAndSM-56ERA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwP9GvledGXfo94cwU-BwSlKB3KQH_1_6fiZAW8j0lNsA&amp;oe=69C8EBFB" alt="Instagram billede fra @hellooks" /></p><p><strong>@hellooks</strong></p><p>Erja, 38 &amp; Lennart, 2<br/>
<br/>
“I’m wearing an old Fredriksson cap, a Beastie Boys tour t-shirt from the year 1987 and a skirt which used to be a dress. Lennart is wearing Kakara jeans, my old suspenders, and a hat made by me out of vintage Tampella fabric. The t-shirt print is my own design, too.<br/>
For some reason new clothes don’t have the same feeling to them as old ones.”<br/>
<br/>
7 June 2007, Kiasma Art Museum<br/>
<br/>
#hellooks #year2007 #streetstylehelsinki #katutyyli #erjahirvi</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/654197252_18578999941036149_6573984764963554428_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NjY0NjMwNzM2ODIzOTUxMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkxOC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=TCVxlbFH4mEQ7kNvwFwnQ8N&amp;_nc_oc=AdoNvweVEIRG3WS8jVMcwYS1DUu869_yLJCwfeMFNvOtApfaypfw_DJMkaWR3k1S49o&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=sd2RvPcYtCfAndSM-56ERA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwP9GvledGXfo94cwU-BwSlKB3KQH_1_6fiZAW8j0lNsA&amp;oe=69C8EBFB" alt="Instagram billede fra @hellooks" /></p><p><strong>@hellooks</strong></p><p>Erja, 38 &amp; Lennart, 2<br/>
<br/>
“I’m wearing an old Fredriksson cap, a Beastie Boys tour t-shirt from the year 1987 and a skirt which used to be a dress. Lennart is wearing Kakara jeans, my old suspenders, and a hat made by me out of vintage Tampella fabric. The t-shirt print is my own design, too.<br/>
For some reason new clothes don’t have the same feeling to them as old ones.”<br/>
<br/>
7 June 2007, Kiasma Art Museum<br/>
<br/>
#hellooks #year2007 #streetstylehelsinki #katutyyli #erjahirvi</p>]]></content:encoded>
